Enable:
1. Sudo cp interfaces.mesh interfaces ( in /etc/network)
2. modify /etc/hosts
3. Reboot

Disable:
1. Sudo cp interfaces.orig interfaces
(In /etc/network)
2. Modify /etc/hosts
3.Reboot
